            <h2>RMB Global Markets Research calendar            </h2>
            <p>The RMB Global Markets Research calendar will keep you informed of what and when important data will be released, and what to expect.<br />
              <br />
            </p>
            <h3>How the calendar works <br />
            </h3>
            <p>The calendar is broken down into two sections:</p>
            <ul class="flush">
              <li><span class="flushText">The first section contains all the dates for a specific category</span></li>
              <li><span class="flushText">The second section contains individual dates</span></li>
            </ul>
            <p>              You can mix and match multiple categories and individual dates to suit your calendar requirements.<br />
              <br />
            </p>
            <h3>To install these dates in your Outlook</h3>
            <ul class="flush"><li><span class="flushText">Select the categories and/or individual dates you require</span></li>
              <li><span class="flushText">Click on the &quot;generate dates&quot; button and save the file to your computer</span></li>
             <li><span class="flushText">Open the saved file once it has been downloaded</span></li>
              <li><span class="flushText">A pop up window will appear in your Outlook programme, select the categories to be added to your calendar by checking the applicable tick boxes</span></li>
             <li><span class="flushText">Click OK</span></li><br/>
 
